Path of Adventure Privacy Policy
About
This privacy policy governs your use of the software application Path of Adventure ("Application") that was created by Jordin Kee (a.k.a. Alinea Games a.k.a. Keeweed). The Application is a text-based game.
What information does the Application obtain and how is it used?
Anonymous game usage data. For example, how often is a game started and how how often is the game finished. This data is exclusively used to improve the game itself. This data is anonymous and cannot be traced back to individual users.
Contact
If you have any questions about your privacy, please contact me at
jordin@alineagames.com
